squidpony.squidgrid.util

Enum DirectionCardinal

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DirectionCardinal>
      • squidpony.squidgrid.util.DirectionCardinal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DirectionCardinal>, Topology

    public enum DirectionCardinal
extends java.lang.Enum<DirectionCardinal>
implements Topology
    Represents the eight grid directions and the deltaX, deltaY values associated with those directions. Only the four primary edges are represented, along with NONE. The grid referenced has x positive to the right and y positive downwards on screen.
    Author:
    Eben Howard - http://squidpony.com - howard@squidpony.com
